      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical rotating-channel flow confirm solver spatial discretization order.",
      "rationale": "Second-order spatial accuracy verified via manufactured-solution test on a rotating annular channel. Observed order of accuracy 1.94, consistent with nominal second-order scheme. Requirement met."
