      "rationale": "Validation dataset obtained from the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow and speed conditions. Fluid is a glycerol-saline blood analog with matched viscosity and density. Validation activities directly representative of COU. Requirement met."
    },
    {
